{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_013ATJJd2c2XKax7GrrEBAb6","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01MEivVCGbXwyq9zc77GmUUX","name":"Agent","input":{"description":"Read Top 3 Opportunities sheet","prompt":"Read the Excel workbook at \"C:/Users/rjega/vendor-spend-analysis/outputs/A - TEMPLATE - RWA - Vendor Spend Strategy (R Jegadeswari).xlsx\" and return the full content (all cells, column headers, row structure, and any instruction text) of ONLY the sheet named \"Top 3 Opportunities\". \n\nReturn:\n1. The sheet name exactly as it appears\n2. Every cell value including cell address, e.g. A1=\"...\", B1=\"...\", etc.\n3. All column headers in row 1 (or wherever they appear)\n4. Any instruction text (especially in A1)\n5. The exact structure (how many columns, what they're named)\n\nDo NOT read any other sheet. Use a script to read the workbook via Node.js with the xlsx library, or use Python with openpyxl. Run the script to get the actual data.\n\nUse this Node.js script approach:\n```\nconst XLSX = require('C:/Users/rjega/vendor-spend-analysis/node_modules/xlsx');\nconst wb = XLSX.readFile('C:/Users/rjega/vendor-spend-analysis/outputs/A - TEMPLATE - RWA - Vendor Spend Strategy (R Jegadeswari).xlsx');\nconst sheetNames = wb.SheetNames;\nconsole.log('Sheet names:', sheetNames);\n// Find sheet with \"Top 3\" or \"Opportunities\" in name\nconst targetSheet = sheetNames.find(n => n.includes('Top') || n.includes('Opportunit'));\nconsole.log('Target sheet:', targetSheet);\nconst ws = wb.Sheets[targetSheet];\nconsole.log('Sheet data:', JSON.stringify(ws, null, 2));\n```\n\nRun this script and return all output.","subagent_type":"general-purpose"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":16950,"cache_read_input_tokens":16503,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":16950,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"5bcc7f87-eb01-404c-a2a2-f65f33ff6949","uuid":"ed0140bb-be1a-42ec-8729-e504b9aa458d"}
